{"tid":1798722,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【香 港 出 路 只 有 支 爆】（長文）","createTime":"2019-12-26T12:09:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-13T18:00:27.000Z","uid":100155,"like":24,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"c8c8989d67342d75e7cd36acda18d63640a459e8","tid":1798722,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:09:09.000Z","msg":"(我將篇文save左做圖方便流傳）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/v7YqHKC.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fv7YqHKC.png&h=a8425d6c&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"581f6e844178fdf27d0dc88425896a2235e8abd4","tid":1798722,"uid":100155,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:10:14.000Z","msg":"2. 攬炒阻止香港幫中共回血<br />\n呢個其實我無實質idea,但方向可能包括：<br />\n&bull; 阻止中資喺香港融資及IPO；<br />\n&bull; 阻止大量公帑透過大白象項目送比中國contractor（要短期內阻止到，可能真係要先喺2020立法會開始入手）；<br />\n&bull; 阻止中共用港幣換外匯。<br />\n<br />\n3. 國際線<br />\n路透社早前透露中紀委命令港府推行送中條例 &ndash; 又一被中共干預嘅例子<br />\n人權：香港警暴殺人肆虐、被自殺輪姦酷刑虐待集中營、維吾爾集中營、西藏大屠殺、<br />\nConnect外國民眾：NBA、英超（奧燒）、Blizzard等<br />\n<br />\n中共點樣利用香港走法律罅去做違法行為：<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1729711\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1729711</a><br />\n<br />\n德國政府同World Bank等一直資助中國發展、每年送幾十億歐羅+美金，呢啲錢＝幫中國發展AI監控、集中營、華為5G間諜網絡、補貼國企外貿、改建航母、喺南海起軍事基地、研發各種導彈等"},{"pid":"1c568076e6d4b69810298fb9906fbcc7f4b47325","tid":1798722,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:10:40.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3cb0ac346932d21603dc965b6064ecbe081e7fa2","tid":1798722,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:10:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"22d06f032a821b70dc9953f0dc1e5387ed26e0f7","tid":1798722,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:10:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"775f556b22a1db38c47885c2f2ff5fb9df513b0f","tid":1798722,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:11:00.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"62f51a2fb25feb8bb69eee25ce1e9fda7ea5882c","tid":1798722,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"22d06f032a821b70dc9953f0dc1e5387ed26e0f7","tid":1798722,"uid":327740,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:10:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:11:15.000Z","msg":"g持"},{"pid":"3d3a93e57268469fb960539648569457b194196f","tid":1798722,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:11:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a4019b3dc467c0cd30c8b3d24b3db93c0b98817c","tid":1798722,"uid":100155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:12:13.000Z","msg":"你想有五大訴求真自治。你想香港獨立。但中共政權會就咁袖手旁觀、比我地有民選立法會、民選特首、甚至獨立主權？<br />\n<br />\n中共一日仲存在，香港（仲有維吾爾、西藏、台灣）嘅人都唔會有好日子過。"},{"pid":"b5bd774597224990a5c9fcf166dca0455ae6938d","tid":1798722,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"51c832f565aa1554476212a26f3e1eb2dad7d119","tid":1798722,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">支爆近了，大限將至；<br />\n只有七十，沒有七一。<br />\n<br />\n黃天當立，亡國者習；<br />\n歲在庚子，天下大吉。</span>"},{"pid":"51f576de2df7031cdb2d09574b3be22a6a8ebe47","tid":1798722,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:12:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b07cb6f5f760b76bef70ffb65bd6441d3621660e","tid":1798722,"uid":100155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"51c832f565aa1554476212a26f3e1eb2dad7d119","tid":1798722,"uid":269515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:12:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: orange;\">支爆近了，大限將至；<br />\n只有七十，沒有七一。<br />\n<br />\n黃天當立，亡國者習；<br />\n歲在庚子，天下大吉。</span>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-26T12:12:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/